📱 Contact Management Application

A professional-grade contact management system designed for efficient contact organization and management. Built with modern web technologies to provide a seamless user experience across all devices.or A modern, responsive contact management application built with React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS. Features complete CRUD operations, real-time search, data validation, and professional UI design.


## ✨ Key Highlights

🎯 **Complete Contact Management** - Full CRUD operations with intuitive interface
🔍 **Smart Search & Filtering** - Real-time search across all contact fields
✅ **Robust Data Validation** - Comprehensive form validation with duplicate prevention
📱 **Fully Responsive** - Optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices
💾 **Persistent Storage** - Browser localStorage for data persistence
🎨 **Modern UI/UX** - Clean, professional design with smooth animations
⚡ **High Performance** - Built with Vite for fast development and optimized builds

## 🛠️ Technical Stack

- **Frontend**: React 18 + TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Build Tool**: Vite
- **Storage**: Browser localStorage
- **Validation**: Custom validation utilities

## 🚀 Features

### Core Functionality
- ➕ Add new contacts with comprehensive form validation
- ✏️ Edit existing contacts with pre-populated data
- 🗑️ Delete contacts with confirmation dialog
- 👀 View all contacts in organized card layout

### Advanced Features
- 🔍 Real-time search across all contact fields
- 📊 Sort by name, email, or date added
- 🚫 Duplicate email prevention
- 📱 Responsive design for all screen sizes
- ⚡ Fast, smooth animations and transitions

### Data Management
- 📧 Email format validation
- 📞 Phone number format validation
- 🏠 Address validation
- 💾 Automatic data persistence
- 🔄 Real-time updates

